- added ::Gtk2::FormFactory::ComboBox
- added ::Gtk2::List::Simple

0.06.1
- GtkAssistant can construct pages using a custom class in an array coercion

0.06
- added GtkAssistant trait
- added GtkAssistantPage meta-object
